=== Noun ===
1.  The [[status]] of something: ''She check to see what kind of shape the animal was in.''<br>
2.  The appearance of something, especially it's outline:  ''He was pear-shaped.''<br>
3.  A figure with unspecified appearance: ''What shape shall we use for the cookies?  Stars, circles, or diamonds?''


